@startuml seq-trusted-contact
!theme plain
title Sequence — Người thân tin cậy (Trusted Contact emergency)

actor Patient
participant "PatientMobile" as PM
participant "Backend\n+ Relayer" as Backend
participant "ConsentLedger" as Contract
participant "TCMobile" as TM
actor TC

== Phase A: Patient đăng ký TC ==

Patient -> PM : Thêm người thân tin cậy\n(paste ví TC + label "Mẹ")
PM -> Patient : Biometric MFA
PM -> PM : Sign TrustedContactPermit\n(EIP-712)
PM -> Backend : POST /api/relayer/trusted-contact
Backend -> Contract : setTrustedContactBySig(...)\n(sponsored)
Contract -> Contract : isTrustedContact[P][TC] = true\nemit TrustedContactSet

PM -> PM : runEncryptionCeremony(TC)\n(encrypt mọi record's AES key\ncho TC's NaCl pubkey)
PM -> Backend : POST /api/key-share/bulk-trusted-contact
Backend -> Backend : Lưu KeyShare rows\nsource='trusted-contact'

== Phase A+: Auto pre-share record mới ==

Patient -> PM : Tạo record mới
PM -> Backend : registerRecord + autoPreShareNewRecord
note right of PM : Encrypt cho mỗi TC active\nGửi /api/key-share/bulk-trusted-contact

== Phase B: TC truy cập khẩn cấp ==

TC -> TM : Login app + mở record của Patient
TM -> Backend : GET /api/key-share/record/:cidHash
Backend -> Contract : canAccess(P, TC, cidHash)
Contract -> Contract : isTrustedContact[P][TC]?
note right of Contract : Footgun #2 fix:\nreturn TRUE ngay
Contract --> Backend : true
Backend -> Backend : Defensive check\nTrustedContact table\n(commit 3e53fcf)
Backend --> TM : encryptedPayload
TM -> TM : decrypt NaCl box\nthen AES (IPFS ciphertext)
TM -> TC : Render record

== Phase C: Patient thu hồi TC ==

Patient -> PM : Thu hồi TC
PM -> PM : Sign TrustedContactPermit(false)
PM -> Backend : POST /api/relayer/trusted-contact
Backend -> Contract : setTrustedContactBySig(active=false)
Contract -> Contract : isTrustedContact[P][TC] = false\nemit TrustedContactRevoked

Backend -> Backend : handleTrustedContactRevoked:\nmark status='revoked'\ncascade revoke KeyShare rows\nsource='trusted-contact'

TC -> TM : Mở record (sau khi revoke)
TM -> Backend : GET /api/key-share/record/:cidHash
Backend -> Contract : canAccess?
Contract --> Backend : false (TC revoked + no consent)
Backend --> TM : 403 Forbidden

note over TC : TC vẫn có thể decrypt OFFLINE\nnếu local cache còn (limitation\nenvelope encryption — không\nthể un-share data đã decrypt)

@enduml
